<h3>The Content Nobody Else Is Posting</h3>
<p>Employee-shared content drives <strong>8x higher engagement</strong> than brand-channel content. Encourage your sales team to post their own vehicle walkarounds, customer delivery moments, and car tips on their personal accounts.</p>
<p>72% of dealership employees are missing social selling opportunities. An employee advocacy program turns every salesperson into a micro-influencer for your dealership.</p>
